Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.68,0:01:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類因人口膨脹而向宇宙移民已過了半個世紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.95,0:01:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球周圍漂浮著巨大的人工都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為人類的「第二故鄉」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.04,0:01:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們就在這裏出生、成長、生兒育女\N並走向死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世紀0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.62,0:02:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離地球最遠的宇宙都市SIDE 3\N以ZION公國之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.00,0:02:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球聯邦政府發起了獨立戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.21,0:02:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在開始一個月的戰鬥裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.59,0:02:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公國和地球聯邦軍有半數以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.07,0:02:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們對於自己的行為產生了恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『逃離月神二號作戰』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.78,0:02:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巡洋艦 瑪達加斯加號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.42,0:02:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.72,0:02:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入港基準速度左舷2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.09,0:02:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方向正確！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.99,0:02:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,White Base已經入港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各人員馬上回崗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武器填充組立即集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.96,0:03:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總務人員請問在那裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做好接待母艦的準備沒有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切準備妥當！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各人員在母艦停泊後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.17,0:03:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上做整備工作！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.48,0:03:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.75,0:03:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母艦上有一百個以上的百姓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為SIDE 7號受襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才會到來月神二號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.52,0:03:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果可以的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.69,0:03:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想收容他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.32,0:03:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是月神二號也在一級戒備狀態下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾經艱苦才來到的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.63,0:03:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然不肯收留我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎會有這種事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於你這個問題，讓我來回答！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是月神二號基地司令馬健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.31,0:03:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就是布萊特君？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.24,0:03:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民們非常疲倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你們可以收容艦上全部人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一直在逃避ZION軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就沒好好休息過！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏沒有多餘地方去收留百姓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒可能吧...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.40,0:04:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我要各位留在此地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.47,0:04:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等待地球聯邦軍有指示後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.91,0:04:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才可安排大家返回地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.24,0:04:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎麼行...？想回去啊...！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我宣佈的人名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要和其它難民隔開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.82,0:04:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特·諾亞、米萊·八洲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.32,0:04:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良·保政，雪拉·瑪斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.66,0:04:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱·西登、隼人·小林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅·雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼！把哥哥們怎樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.64,0:04:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請告訴我這是什麼意思...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仕官侯補生和平民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.57,0:04:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擅自使用軍隊秘密武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.21,0:04:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即是指使用White Base和GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.58,0:05:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們準備會受到軍事審判吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.35,0:05:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,White Base沒收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.12,0:05:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GUNDAM將受到封閉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.92,0:05:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歸回我們軍隊管理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連當時SIDE 7號是狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.93,0:05:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不去查清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.16,0:05:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然向我們說這番說話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是司令官，馬健！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.88,0:05:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你收留母艦及百姓們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.79,0:05:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會處理一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.05,0:05:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請安心在此養傷吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.37,0:05:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待會封好GUNDAM就輪到鋼坦克了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼坦克怎處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙已經損壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快做吧！否則司令又要罵了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION軍會來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.03,0:06:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那『紅色彗星』夏亞絕對不會放棄追蹤母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如封閉了GUNDAM的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.92,0:06:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒資格和我說戰略的問題！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.59,0:06:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本不知道『紅色彗星』的利害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的不是正規軍人的判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才覺這樣想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過『紅色彗星』這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個有名的戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.37,0:06:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是不會做以一隻姆沙爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便來挑戰我們月神二號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.84,0:06:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種愚蠢行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.04,0:06:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們似乎仍未被雷達深測到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.97,0:06:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一帶的米諸夫斯基粒子很濃厚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.57,0:07:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人就在附近居然仍未探出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.94,0:07:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是奇妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.41,0:07:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現代戰爭發展到某個階段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.41,0:07:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能又會回復到古時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面對面那種接近戰也說不定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，你想毀滅月神二號？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.75,0:07:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中尉，你會贊成嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.25,0:07:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月神二號是擁有龐大建設的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍事家的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.43,0:07:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定不會相信會以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這姆沙爾級戰艦去攻擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們才去攻擊他們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.40,0:07:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是有對策的，杜力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.40,0:07:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祝你成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時的那個女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是十年前失散了的妹妹...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.62,0:07:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.40,0:07:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如是亞路佩西雅的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她太勇敢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放下它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.70,0:08:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再動的話我便開槍了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.28,0:08:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定不是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞路佩西雅是個很溫柔的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用太空服潛入敵軍基地！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.53,0:08:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一個目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.36,0:08:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是奪取聯邦軍的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.40,0:08:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二個目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.43,0:08:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是要奪取那艘母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.87,0:08:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假如失敗的話就要破壞它們！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.78,0:08:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飯來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.48,0:08:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，我要見馬健司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.12,0:08:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你怎麼該也是沒用的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能肯定夏亞一定不會來襲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.76,0:09:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話雖如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.63,0:09:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是不先填飽肚子不成啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有得吃時不吃飽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算有事時甚麼也做不來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.87,0:09:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.27,0:09:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱說得對，阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.84,0:09:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃飯就像子彈放入槍膛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為一個士兵，就算不想吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也必須要吃下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，開始行動嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.19,0:10:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先別急，你看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.66,0:10:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅外線探測器..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心些裝上爆雷別碰到它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.36,0:10:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以我絕不能忘記這雙層構造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.49,0:10:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是和ZION的ZAKU決定性分別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.93,0:10:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...GUNDAM最優勝的是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.74,0:10:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是戰鬥力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和一向的ZAKU不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.47,0:11:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次的戰鬥過程均記錄下來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連戰鬥過程也可記錄？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換句話說GUNDAM
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.25,0:11:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愈作戰得多就愈學會作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.55,0:11:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變得更強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.99,0:11:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！而且連我這個生手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.12,0:11:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可和身經百戰的夏亞打個平手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.66,0:11:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不關乎我的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.56,0:11:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是GUNDAM的教育型計算機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.40,0:11:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,性能太優越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.67,0:11:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太謙虛了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重力裝置壞了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.85,0:11:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來電源部份被毀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.99,0:11:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們竟偷越過了監視雷達網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.64,0:12:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令！相信敵人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.87,0:12:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿太空服的特殊破壞部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和布萊特所說的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.88,0:12:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命令馬劍號出擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快開門！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.80,0:12:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道他們忘了我們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.30,0:12:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可等在這裏下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,門開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.68,0:12:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電源終止連電子鎖也失靈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.51,0:12:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！米萊和雪拉呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.22,0:12:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該在隔壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊、雪拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.53,0:13:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬劍號立即出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.50,0:13:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開穩定鎖！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.88,0:13:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION軍已開始攻擊這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.01,0:13:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何不讓我們到安全地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為司令還未有命令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.65,0:13:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這豈不是叫我們等死？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！我不是這個意思！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.56,0:13:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那請你通知司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他想法子吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.30,0:13:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令現在根本沒時間理會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在幹麼，快過來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快叫大家集合！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.68,0:13:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將White Base駛離軍港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.25,0:13:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅解除GUNDAM封印！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.90,0:13:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬劍號出來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.72,0:15:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好...中伏了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬劍號將出入口塞住？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發動引擎，準備出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.13,0:15:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,良、凱、阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解開GUNDAM封印了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.40,0:15:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別心急，才剛開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，難民呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.81,0:15:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛從重力區正過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.64,0:15:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波正在帶領住他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.48,0:15:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！我現在先去GUNDAM那裏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.45,0:15:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊！待大引擎有足夠動力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便微速前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.73,0:15:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.59,0:15:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令 你沒事吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.43,0:15:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過擦傷一點罷了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰把White Base開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.90,0:15:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駛過去！靠近White Base
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在這裏幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.05,0:16:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經下了命令要封閉它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.79,0:16:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠和夏亞作戰的只有GUNDAM！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.29,0:16:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我命令你立即離開！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我預了要背上叛逆罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.44,0:16:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬健司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的敵人應該是ZION軍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.91,0:16:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是我們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.74,0:16:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.95,0:16:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒時間向你說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.28,0:16:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍隊內軍紀的重要性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上級的命令是絕對不可違背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.45,0:16:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍紀   軍紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.79,0:16:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算有又如何！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍人為守軍法要死是你們的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.02,0:16:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可以叫百姓陪你一起送死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬健司令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.76,0:16:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.63,0:16:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬健君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.83,0:16:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.50,0:17:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽我說，馬健君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.57,0:17:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是White Base
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.47,0:17:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有GUNDAM，鋼坦克和鋼加農
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.24,0:17:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也都是聯邦的秘密武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.18,0:17:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在唯有說，最不幸的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.79,0:17:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們用得比我們熟練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.16,0:17:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且已經有兩次的作戰經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...艦長...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.30,0:17:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，他們都是外行人..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.60,0:17:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你身為司令官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.10,0:17:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是有責任幫助他們作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會負上責任的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.18,0:17:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.78,0:17:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會聽艦長你的吩咐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.07,0:18:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬殊，希司，你們聽著！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.51,0:18:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要潛入去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.81,0:18:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一口氣將木馬型戰艦及機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.58,0:18:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部破壞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.71,0:18:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.75,0:18:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.94,0:19:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬健司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.54,0:19:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若不移開馬劍號的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.38,0:19:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母艦是不可能出港的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.55,0:19:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去，未作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.95,0:19:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有的戰艦也會覆沒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.59,0:19:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是姆沙爾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.47,0:19:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊沉馬劍號吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.44,0:19:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.51,0:19:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把母艦固定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.41,0:19:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,預備防爆措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.54,0:19:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備母艦主炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.83,0:19:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放下防爆罩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.31,0:20:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞄準馬劍號內的反應爐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.78,0:20:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家做好衝擊的防衛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，快離開港口通道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開炮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.98,0:21:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.52,0:21:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是個怎樣的人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.23,0:21:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長，我們成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.32,0:21:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.12,0:21:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.39,0:21:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起碼在回地球前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.39,0:21:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就交給他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.30,0:21:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是艦長的遺願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.43,0:21:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.97,0:21:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在和ZION軍交戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.60,0:22:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇上困難重重時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.40,0:22:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,值得讓我們學習的前輩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.21,0:22:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻相繼離我們而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.74,0:22:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不覺得這是個冷酷的時代嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.46,0:22:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長，你的White Base
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.20,0:22:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一定會親手送回地球的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.09,0:22:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.49,0:23:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底在那裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.04,0:23:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果隨著重力墜落就會燃燒殆盡的大氣圈突入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.51,0:23:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這瞬間夏亞對White Base發動奇襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.69,0:23:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵我雙方都處於危險
